                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17860719-18-defend255 t17860719-18-punish87"></join>
               Whipped
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury before Mr. Justice HEATH.</p>
